alue here, and the timing is perfect: getting the marketing and brand right=
 before July is going to be key to the success in-stores.=C2=A0</p>
<p dir=3D"ltr">Here&#39;s what I&#39;d suggest. For the first three months =
of the launch =E2=80=94 the period where everything matters most =E2=80=94 =
I&#39;d recommend a package of 4 x 1-hour sessions per month at R2,000 per =
session (R8,000/month). That cadence keeps us close enough to
 actually build things and adjust in real time, rather than just talking on=
ce a month.</p>
<p dir=3D"ltr">The whole point is to take pressure off you so you can stay =
focused on sales, production and keeping the Checkers relationship strong. =
Concretely, here&#39;s where I&#39;d help:</p>
<ul dir=3D"ltr">
<li dir=3D"ltr"><b>Nail the target audience.</b>=C2=A0We&#39;ll do the pers=
onas-and-occasions exercise together and land on the one or two occasions D=
ona Fuego should own =E2=80=94 so your marketing spend goes narrow and deep=
 instead of broad and expensive. This is the gap you
 named, and it&#39;s the one I can take off your plate fastest.</li><li dir=
=3D"ltr"><b>Build the positioning</b>=C2=A0for Dona Fuego =E2=80=94 getting=
 what&#39;s in your head into something clear and usable, so you&#39;re not=
 staring at a blank slate.</li><li dir=3D"ltr"><b>Design the launch campaig=
n.</b>=C2=A0I&#39;ll help you structure the Field Bar idea end to end =E2=
=80=94 the partnership, the giveaway mechanic, the in-store push =E2=80=94 =
into something simple you can run.</li><li dir=3D"ltr"><b>Set up the &quot;=
1,000 Top Fans&quot; system</b>=C2=A0so you&#39;re capturing customers and =
content from day one, and we can build real campaigns off real fans.</li><l=
i dir=3D"ltr"><b>Bring the Duchess playbook to your PR and partner strategy=
</b>=C2=A0=E2=80=94 go deep with a few partners, drive the algorithm, and t=
urn that into rate of sale you can show.</li><li dir=3D"ltr"><b>Get you rai=
se-ready.</b>=C2=A0When you&#39;re ready, I&#39;ll help build the pitch dec=
k and a basic data room for the tequila brand, and think through landing a =
strategic partner.=C2=A0</li></ul>
<p dir=3D"ltr">And beyond the deliverables =E2=80=94 the independent soundi=
ng board. Someone you can be straight with on the days that feel like &quot=
;what am I doing here,&quot; not just the days on top of the world.</p>
<p dir=3D"ltr">If that works for you, we can get going before the July laun=
ch.</p>
